Nollywood actress, Annie Idibia, has revealed how her husband, the Nigerian singer, Innocent Idibia popularly known as 2face convinced her to model in the video of his song, African Queen. She disclosed this via her Instagram page, expressing that they had no idea the song would change the entire music scene in Africa, as he has recently broke out from a boy band group. The mother of two wrote, “19 years ago, while still struggling to find my feet in the modeling industry, my then-boyfriend who just broke from a boy band group called me to star in his new song (African Queen). How New APC Chairman Will Emerge Nothing Will Bring Me Back To Politics, Says  Obasanjo “We both had no idea the song would change the entire music scene in Africa and it’s narrative and also become the biggest song out of the continent. “Fast forward to 19 years later and almost 10 years married to that amazing rare human artist, we get to do this again! It’s #SmileSeason Guys!”